  <summary date="2021-03-15T23:36:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Emergency Support for Substance Use Disorders Act

This bill requires the Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration to award grants to states, other jurisdictions, and community-based entities for harm reduction activities to address drug misuse during the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) pandemic.</summary>
